scores.description:
List of ORES score objects. Each model uses the model name as a map key and was used to score this revision.  Example: {
  "awesomeness": {
    "model_name": "awesomeness"
    "model_version": "1.0.1",
    "prediction": ["yes", "mostly"],
    "probability": {
      "yes": 0.99,
      "mostly": 0.90,
      "hardly": 0.01
    }
  }
}
